ReportBundle.ReportXML: <Report ReportGID="3d9a2eb0-d52b-4ecd-80ff-52ffcc7a8cfc" ReportUseType="2" ReportType="5" ReportName="Feed vs Milk by Pen" CreatedDT="2013-10-10T22:09:09.627" ModifiedDT="2014-04-09T15:12:28.65" ModifiedBy="VAS" ConcurrencyTS="AAAAAAAAD64=" ReportVersion="0" />

ReportQuery.ReportQueryText: <QueryBundle> <QueryText>select z.* from ( select FEED.ReportDate ,loc.LocationName ,cmp.CompanyName ,pn.PenNumber ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(FEED.TotalAF, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'TotalAF' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(FEED.TotalDM, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'TotalDM' ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(FEED.TargetAF, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'TargetAF' ,FEED.PenCount ,FEED.TotalFeedCost ,dbo.GetMeasurementValue(MILK.TotalMilk, cmp.MediumMeasurementType) as 'TotalMilkSold' ,PW.PenTotalMilk from ( select z.InstanceDate as 'ReportDate' ,z.LocationGID ,z.PenGID ,AVG(z.PenCount) as 'PenCount' ,SUM(z.UnitQuantity) as 'TotalAF' ,SUM(z.UnitQuantityDM) as 'TotalDM' ,SUM(z.TargetUnitQuantity) as 'TargetAF' ,SUM(z.Cost) as 'TotalFeedCost' from ( select fs.InstanceDate ,dl.locationGID ,pn.PenGID ,it.UnitQuantity ,it.UnitQuantity * it.DMPct as UnitQuantityDM ,it.TargetUnitQuantity ,pcc.[Count] as PenCount ,dbo.GetFifoCost(it.UnitQuantity, it.InventoryItemGID, fsmi.SourceLocationGID, it.TransactionDT) as Cost from FeedingScheduleDrop fsd join FeedingScheduleLoad fsl on fsl.FeedingScheduleLoadGID = fsd.FeedingScheduleLoadGID join FeedingScheduleMix fsm on fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID = fsl.FeedingScheduleMixGID join FeedingSchedule fs on fs.FeedingScheduleGID = fsm.FeedingScheduleGID join InventoryTransaction it on it.TransactionSourceGID = fsd.FeedingScheduleDropGID join FeedingScheduleMixInstruction fsmi on fsmi.FeedingScheduleMixGID = fsl.FeedingScheduleMixGID and fsmi.InventoryItemGID = it.InventoryItemGID join Location dl on dl.LocationGID = fsd.LocationGID join Pen pn on pn.LocationGID = fsd.LocationGID join Company cmp on cmp.CompanyGID = dl.CompanyGID cross apply (select top 1 pcc.[Count] from PenCountChange pcc where pcc.PenGID = pn.PenGID and pcc.CreatedDT <= it.TransactionDT and InventoryItemType=3 order by pcc.CreatedDT desc) pcc ) z group by z.InstanceDate, z.LocationGID, z.PenGID ) FEED join Location loc on loc.LocationGID = FEED.LocationGID join Company cmp on cmp.CompanyGID = loc.CompanyGID join Pen pn on pn.LocationGID = loc.LocationGID cross apply (select SUM(it.UnitQuantity) as TotalMilk from Delivery del join InventoryTransaction it on it.InventoryTransactionGID = del.InventoryTransactionGID join InventoryItem ii on ii.InventoryItemGID = it.InventoryItemGID where ii.InventoryItemType = 5 and it.TransactionType = 3 and CONVERT(date, del.DeliveryDT) = FEED.ReportDate) MILK cross apply (select top 1 pw.TotalMilk as 'PenTotalMilk' from ParlorWatchTransaction pw where pw.PenGID = FEED.PenGID and CONVERT(date, pw.TransactionDT) = FEED.ReportDate order by pw.TransactionDT desc) PW ) z where 1=1</QueryText> <PreQueryText /> </QueryBundle>
